weekly_modifiers.name: Tyrannical
weekly_modifiers.description: Bosses have 30% more health. Bosses and their minions inflict up to 15% increased damage.

weekly_modifiers.name: Storming
weekly_modifiers.description: While in combat, enemies periodically summon damaging whirlwinds.

weekly_modifiers.name: Raging
weekly_modifiers.description: Non-boss enemies enrage at 30% health remaining, temporarily granting immunity to crowd control effects.
